snippet.title: Fish Out Of Water! - Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Click to Subscribe: http://bit.ly/HalfbrickYTSubscribe

Fish Out Of Water! -- OUT NOW! 
Download on the App Store: http://apple.co/1dUVZHZ
Gplay Store: http://bit.ly/1TvUUpU

A brand new game from the creators of Fruit Ninja and Jetpack Joyride. 
Fish Out Of Water tells the story of an adventurous cast of characters as they search to see the world from a whole new perspective! These daring companions must juggle constantly changing weather conditions, challenging obstacles and a fussy judging panel to skip across the water in search of perfection!
 
Get ready for a sea of adventure and prepare to go where no fish has gone before!

WATCH!
Behind the Scenes of Fish Out Of Water! http://bit.ly/ZvQbdF
